Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.65,0:02:23.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會忘了帶課本的女生根本沒有活著的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.94,0:02:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萌度  零
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳說什麼  混帳傢伙！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.98,0:02:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.20,0:02:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道妳也沒帶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就用這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然都畫滿塗鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.57,0:02:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話  東野君你就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係  我會跟旁邊的同學一起看的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.74,0:02:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也忘記帶了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一堂課能把位置靠在一起和我一起看嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可…可以是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你該不會是故意的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.12,0:02:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了能接近我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.89,0:02:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來  妳是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢噢  這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.38,0:02:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:02:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後的修行  勇者滿臉通紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.55,0:03:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.14,0:03:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會滿臉通紅呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個…  靠得太近了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該能看清楚的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  皆本
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當同學真是愉快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.87,0:03:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺真新鮮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以來從沒感覺過皆本距離我這麼近
