Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有什麼陰謀..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.80,0:03:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是谷崎先生內心最深處的部分…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒時間了  開始吧
