Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是總是這樣對紫穗說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像這樣和喜歡的東西一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼可愛的我這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來  啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太狡猾了  換我  紫穗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我嘴對嘴餵你吃~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會自己吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本先生  了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:05:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃飽了吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東野君  你又來了
